  "title": "Garlicky Quick Dutch Broccoli Gratin",
  "description": "A quick and flavorful Dutch broccoli gratin recipe with a garlicky twist, perfect for a weeknight dinner.",
  "cuisine": "Dutch",
  "diet": [
    "Sugar-Free",
    "Vegetarian"
  ],
